#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:119
msgid "Side panel"
msgstr "แผงด้านข้าง"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:121
msgid ""
"The side panel is folded by default. Open it by clicking the :icon:`oi-panel-"
