#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:193
msgid ""
"The order number can be found at the top of the customer's :doc:`receipt <../"
"use/receipts>`."
msgstr ""
"หมายเลขคำสั่งซื้อสามารถพบได้ที่ด้านบนของ:doc:`ใบเสร็จรับเงิน <../use/receipts>`ของลูกค้า"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/extra/preparation.rst:194
msgid ""
"To use the order status screen, log in via a web browser on a mobile device "
